next.data: Browse away to your amusement, and feel free to add some quotes yourself.

children.data: If you like or dislike a quote, vote with the + and - links.  If you feel that the quote doesn't deserve to be in the database at all, click its [X] link next to it; while the quote will not be removed from the database immediately, it will be resubmitted for review, and it is possible that it will be removed.

next.data: Queue now at zero. Fixed PHP encoding issues that caused some quotes to not be displayed. Changed voting button behavior to popup instead of browsing away. Blocking the popups will not affect your ability to vote.
fixed modding.  We also changed the behavior of the "latest quotes" function to display the most recently approved quotes, irrespective of the order it was submitted.
